	* aws-url.adb:
	(Code): new procedure.
	(Hex_Escape): new constant array.
	(Encode): encode all characters not only spaces.

	* aws-response.ads:
	(Data): is now a controlled type to be able to free the memory
	 used for the binary data.
	(Adjust): new procedure.
	(Finalize): new procedure.
	
